  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "According to [solidity-idiosyncrasies](https://github.com/miguelmota/solidity-idiosyncrasies) bellow example is safe to use.\r\n```\r\nfunction safeRemoveAtIndex(uint index) returns (uint[]) {\r\n        if (index >= array.length) return;\r\n\r\n        for (uint i = index; i < array.length-1; i++) {\r\n            array[i] = array[i+1];\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        delete array[array.length-1];\r\n        array.length--;\r\n\r\n        return array;\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n`remix-analyzer/deleteFromDynamicArray` still considers this as unsafe.",
